1
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:07,940
Dayou,

2
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,260
you've been looking out for me
since we were kids.

3
00:00:11,960 --> 00:00:13,420
If there's any work
that makes good money,

4
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:14,740
you gotta bring me along.

5
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:17,620
You're up for anything?

6
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:18,820
Anything!

7
00:00:22,080 --> 00:00:23,500
What about killing a man?

8
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:34,400
[In the Name of Justice]

9
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:37,400
[Episode 20]

10
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:43,460
Is there a cop called Yang Jing

11
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,740
at the Pingshan Development Zone

12
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:48,260
Sub-Bureau?

13
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,220
Yang… Yang Jing?

14
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,300
Yeah.

15
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,180
Why are you blushing?

16
00:02:59,120 --> 00:02:59,620
I'm blushing?

17
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,540
I'm just flushed from the sun.
It's scorching.

18
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,220
Your brother

19
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,660
contacted her a few times
before he died.

20
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,660
He knew about me and Yang…

21
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,300
Wait,

22
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,820
my brother?
Why would my brother go to her?

23
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,220
I don't know,

24
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,300
that's why I want to ask her

25
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:25,380
face to face.

26
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:26,900
Can you arrange that?

27
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,300
Rest assured.

28
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:29,540
As long as I'm there,

29
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,180
she'll answer all your questions.

30
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:33,900
Give us some room.

31
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,940
Please wait outside.

32
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,420
Why do you want me to leave?

33
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,820
I won't say a word
as long as you're here.

34
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:58,340
Hong Liang,

35
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,020
right?

36
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:01,860
Yes.

37
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,060
From Haizhou?

38
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:04,780
Yes.

39
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,140
Were you with the Guidance Group?

40
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:06,660
Yes,

41
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:07,780
but it's disbanded now.

42
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:08,620
How did you find out

43
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:10,020
I talked to Zhenxing on the phone?

44
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:11,460
It was quite a while ago.

45
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,620
Was I under surveillance?

46
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,860
So Zhenxing was under surveillance then.

47
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,580
Well, I got access

48
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,300
to Zhenxing's call records

49
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,340
dating back quite a while before he died

50
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:26,820
through my superior,

51
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,060
so it was all legal.

52
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,660
The Guidance Group has been disbanded,

53
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,780
so why are you still digging into this?

54
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,740
I'm not doing it
as a member of the Guidance Group.

55
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,340
Then why are you
investigating this on your own?

56
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,260
I'm just curious.

57
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,780
I'm a bit of a gossip, okay?

58
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:43,260
Get out!

59
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,180
I'm not here for gossip.

60
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,460
Zhenxing was a great friend of mine.

61
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:58,940
I can't accept that

62
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:01,220
he just died like that.

63
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:03,780
I just want to know

64
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,100
if there's anything
he hasn't accomplished,

65
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,340
and see if I can finish them for him.

66
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:11,940
I just want to see

67
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,020
if I can help him

68
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:15,820
fulfill his last wishes.

69
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,820
Mr. Qiao has been here too.

70
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,740
We didn't just talk on the phone,
we met in person

71
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:33,940
right here.

72
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,460
That's my dad

73
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,340
and my mom.

74
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,380
My mom

75
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,380
was always sick

76
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,820
and she passed away a few years ago.

77
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,020
I'm really sorry.

78
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,220
My dad

79
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,580
passed away young.

80
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:19,220
Someone shot him.

81
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,820
May I ask what was his occupation?

82
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,540
He was an accountant.

83
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,340
How did it happen?

84
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,500
There was a robbery
at the finance office.

85
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,460
And, did they catch the robbers?

86
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:40,980
They caught them within days.

87
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,700
The shooter was sentenced to death

88
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,780
and executed immediately.

89
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:49,700
I was just a kid when my dad died.

90
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,540
I was

91
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:52,980
only 12.

92
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,100
So it's been over a decade?

93
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,420
Which year was that?

94
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:00,700
It was 13 years ago.

95
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:11,780
Yang,

96
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:14,380
may I ask which company was your dad

97
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,260
working for

98
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,300
when it happened?

99
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,260
Wanchuan Mining,

100
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,580
Wan Hai's mine.

101
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:25,500
I see.

102
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:28,540
Was your dad the accountant

103
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:31,220
who passed away

104
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,620
after being wounded by ricochets

105
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:34,580
in the Wanchuan Mining Shooting
13 years ago?

106
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:35,380
Yes.

107
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:39,220
So, did Qiao come to pay his respects
to your dad,

108
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:43,140
or… or was he here
to ask about that case?

109
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,340
But, that was an ironclad case.

110
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,220
Did Qiao Zhenxing

111
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,780
say anything else to you?

112
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,580
He

113
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,220
just paid respects to my parents.

114
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:12,860
I'm sorry.

115
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,220
We messed up that case.

116
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,700
We got

117
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,780
the wrong shooter.

118
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,180
Mr. Qiao.

119
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,380
Mr. Qiao,

120
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,860
what do you mean?

121
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:53,660
I got it wrong.

122
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:56,700
I got it wrong.

123
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:03,460
Later, he called me and told me

124
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:06,300
not to tell anyone about this,

125
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:08,940
especially Qin Feng.

126
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,260
He said he would come to me again,

127
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,860
but then he died.

128
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:33,560
[Dongping Municipal
People's Procuratorate]

129
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:35,900
Why?

130
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:37,740
Didn't I tell you

131
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,140
I want to reopen the case?

132
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,140
Reopen the case?

133
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:44,940
But why do you want to
look into Wang Yu?

134
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:47,180
If you want to pull four years
of his call records,

135
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,580
it will be officially logged.

136
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,620
Just follow the procedure,

137
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:51,420
and I'll approve it.

138
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:54,660
Mr. Li,

139
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:56,620
on what basis?

140
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,300
The case is already closed.

141
00:10:07,920 --> 00:10:08,580
I'm filing an appeal.

142
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,380
I have some new evidence.

143
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:25,660
Okay,

144
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,140
I'll handle it right away.

145
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:51,600
[Dongping Wanchuan
Mining Industry Group Co., Ltd.]

146
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:55,300
This way, please.

147
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,180
Ms. Liu,

148
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,620
thank you for coming.

149
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:11,980
Ms. Liu.

150
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:12,780
Let me introduce you:

151
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:16,020
this is Mr. Wan Hong
from Wanchuan Mining,

152
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,700
and this is Mr. Chen Shenglong

153
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,060
from Tianlong Company.

154
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:19,860
Hello, Mr. Chen.

155
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,540
Mr. Wan, nice to meet you at last.

156
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,260
I've heard a lot about you.

157
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:24,300
Sir, I know your time is precious.

158
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,220
So Mr. Chen, please follow me.

159
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,540
Let me give you a tour of the mine.

160
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:28,980
So,

161
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:32,020
the first thing you see here

162
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:33,980
is the freight yard.

163
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:35,460
This is where

164
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,500
the processed ore is stored

165
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,180
before transportation.

166
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,140
Let me tell you,

167
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:40,980
a few years ago

168
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:43,140
this place was running 24/7,

169
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:44,220
even the nights were as bright as day.

170
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:46,220
It looks like it has been shut down
for a while.

171
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,820
Yeah. I know.

172
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:51,860
That's why Ms. Liu brought you here.

173
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,820
I hope

174
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:54,740
we can turn things around

175
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,500
and build a great partnership.

176
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,820
Mr. Chen, please follow me inside.

177
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:01,100
I'll show you around
the inside of the mine.

178
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,340
Mr. Chen, watch your step.

179
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:03,940
Zijian, keep up.

180
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:05,500
It's really a shame

181
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:07,780
this mine has been shut down

182
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:08,940
for the past few years.

183
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:10,860
Once this mine is back in full swing…

184
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:11,900
Ms. Liu knows,

185
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,340
our output used to be

186
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:15,380
top-notch in all of Dongping.

187
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:17,460
The equipment hasn't been turned on
for three years,

188
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,100
can it still work?

189
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,140
Of course!

190
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,260
Let me tell you,

191
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,140
we spent a lot

192
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:23,140
on the equipment.

193
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:23,540
This way.

194
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:24,740
Just a quick tweak

195
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:26,140
and it'll be good to go.

196
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:27,700
Here, give it to me.

197
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:29,900
This way, please.

198
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:40,960
[Intermediate People's Court]

199
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,520
[Procuratorate
Haidong Provincial Procuratorate Work ID]

200
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:52,540
Just a moment.

201
00:12:58,760 --> 00:12:59,580
Listen up,

202
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,180
we have decided to set up

203
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:03,900
a Special Review Team
for the Wanchuan Mining Shooting,

204
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:06,240
with Xie Hongfei as the unit chief,

205
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:08,160
[Thirteen Years Ago]

206
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,540
and the three of you as members.

207
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:11,940
Take note,

208
00:13:12,520 --> 00:13:15,020
this is a high-profile homicide case.

209
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,820
Assigning it to you

210
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,700
is both a sign of trust

211
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,060
and a challenge.

212
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:22,420
This will also be

213
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:24,060
your first independent case

214
00:13:24,640 --> 00:13:25,740
as prosecutors.

215
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,140
I'm counting on you

216
00:13:29,160 --> 00:13:30,340
not to let us down.

217
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,460
Here's the case file you requested.

218
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:40,900
Thanks.

219
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:41,540
Take your time.

220
00:13:56,280 --> 00:14:01,520
[Criminal Investigation Case File]

221
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:02,060
My dad

222
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,380
was shot.

223
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,960
[Criminal Investigation Case File]

224
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:12,000
[List of Documents in the Case File]

225
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:14,360
[Case Acceptance Registration Form]

226
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:16,000
That's everything.

227
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:16,760
[Thirteen Years Ago
Wanchuan Mining's Finance Office]

228
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:17,180
Thank you, Su.

229
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:17,820
Count it.

230
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,380
Here, please sign there.

231
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:22,900
Zheng,

232
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,260
let's go get a drink later.

233
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:24,880
My treat.

234
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:26,040
[Yang Zheng
Wanchuan Mining's Accountant]

235
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:27,260
I can't tonight.

236
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,900
The miners came out late

237
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,780
and are still in the shower.

238
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,260
I have to wait and pay them.

239
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:33,140
I'll just wait for you.

240
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:04,940
What are you doing?

241
00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:08,460
According to the police investigation,

242
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:10,740
suspects Sun Yihu and Wang Dayou,

243
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,180
both unemployed,

244
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:14,820
robbed the finance office

245
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:16,740
of Wanchuan Mining

246
00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:19,260
on the night of January 31st,
13 years ago,

247
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:22,100
resulting in two deaths
and one critically injured individual

248
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:24,180
who later died.

249
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:25,340
Upon review,

250
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:27,180
the Court finds the facts to be clear

251
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,100
and the evidence conclusive.

252
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:29,980
The defendant's confession
stands undisputed.

253
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:32,380
Taking into account
the serious disruption

254
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,180
to public security and social order,

255
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:36,660
Sun Yihu is sentenced to death

256
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:38,100
and stripped of political rights
for life.

257
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,420
Sun Yihu, do you have any last words?

258
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:42,540
Sign here.

259
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,860
The suspect has been identified.

260
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:48,940
Take him away.

261
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:57,240
[Suspect Information File
Sun Yihu]

262
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,740
I'm sorry.

263
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:03,620
We made a mistake with that case.

264
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:06,100
Sun Yihu

265
00:16:07,160 --> 00:16:08,540
might not have been the shooter.

266
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:11,380
His last name is Gong?

267
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,660
Is that really what he said?

268
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,980
He's disowning his own parents?

269
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,340
Go ask him if his real last name is Sun.

270
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:22,080
[Suspect Information File
Sun Yihu]

271
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:24,820
I believe that

272
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:27,300
as long as you collaborate,

273
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:28,540
this company

274
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:30,540
can overcome its difficulties

275
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:31,940
and turn a profit.

276
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:34,220
Mr. Wan,

277
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,580
what do you think?

278
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:37,340
Alright,

279
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:39,300
since Ms. Liu has asked me,

280
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:41,740
I'll just say a few words

281
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:43,780
about my thoughts on our cooperation.

282
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:45,420
I propose that

283
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:47,100
Tianlong Company

284
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:49,300
participate by investing capital,

285
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:52,060
in exchange for an equity stake.

286
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,660
We can discuss

287
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,700
